How to become verified:<br />
<ol>
<li>
Submit a translation test in the ProZ
<a href="http://www.proz.com/screening-platform/apply?cid=1197983">
testing centre</a>.
The tests are currently available only in select language pairs.
</li>
<li>
Show evidence of recognized translation certification
such as Proz.com Certified PRO, ATA, ITI or CIOL
(this is the fastest option).
</li>
<li>
Start translating and deliver high-quality work.
